  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;In the absence of a suitable undertaking to secure that the occupiers of the new residential units would not be able to apply for on street parking permits, the proposals would have an adverse impact on street parking conditions, highway safety,&amp;nbsp; sustainable modes of transport and would contribute to congestion in the surrounding area contrary to the limitations set out in AA.2. (a) of Class AA of Part 20 of Schedule 2 of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 (as amended).&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The external appearance of the building, including the design and architectural features of the principal elevation is not in keeping with the host building and local character. This is contrary to the limitations set out in AA.2. (e) of Class AA of Part 20 of Schedule 2 of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 (as amended).&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The building would be within 3 km of the perimeter of an aerodrome, which is used by aircraft engaged in the public transport of passengers, contrary to the limitations set out in (o)(vii) and is contrary to the limitations set out in AA.1 (o) and AA.2. (b) . Thus, the proposed development would be contrary to Schedule 2, Part 20, Class AA of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 (as amended).&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
